'''高氙酸盐'''是[[高氙酸|高氙酸]]（[[氢|H]]<sub>4</sub>[[氙|Xe]][[氧|O]]<sub>6</sub>）所成的[[盐_(化学)|盐]]，含有黄色<ref name="cotton1" />的'''高氙酸根'''离子——XeO<sub>6</sub><sup>4−</sup>。<ref name="wiberg">{{Holleman&Wiberg|page=399}}</ref>由[[拉曼光谱|拉曼光谱]]确定这种阴离子为[[八面体形分子构型|八面体形分子构型]], O–Xe–O 键角在87°至 93°之间。<ref>{{Cite journal| last1 = Peterson | first1 = J. L.| last2 = Claassen | first2 = H. H.| last3 = Appelman | first3 = E. H.| title = Vibrational spectra and structures of xenate(VI) and perxenate(VIII) ions in aqueous solution| journal = Inorganic Chemistry | volume = 9| issue = 3| pages = 619–621 | date=March 1970 | doi = 10.1021/ic50085a037}}</ref> 其中的Xe–O键长已通过X射线晶体学确认，为 1.875 Å。<ref name="hamilton1963">{{Cite journal | author1 = Hamilton| last3 = MacKenzie| last2 = Ibers | first2 = J. | first3 = D. | title = Geometry of the Perxenate Ion | journal = Science | volume = 141 | issue = 3580 | pages = 532–534 | date=Aug 1963 | issn = 0036-8075 | pmid = 17738629 | doi = 10.1126/science.141.3580.532|bibcode = 1963Sci...141..532H }}</ref>

== 制备==
高氙酸盐是通过[[三氧化氙|三氧化氙]]在强碱中[[歧化|歧化]]而成的：<ref name="harding2002">{{cite book
| title = Elements of the ''p'' Block |volume=9 |series=Molecular World
| first1= Charlie |last1=Harding
| first2= David Arthur |last2=Johnson
| first3= Rob |last3=Janes
| publisher = Royal Society of Chemistry
| year = 2002
| isbn = 0-85404-690-9
| page = 93
}}</ref>
:2 XeO<sub>3</sub> ({{abbr|s|solid}}) + 4 OH<sup>−</sup> ({{abbr|aq|aqueous solution}}) → Xe ({{abbr|g|gas}}) + {{chem|XeO|6|4-}} ({{abbr|aq|aqueous solution}}) + O<sub>2</sub> ({{abbr|g|gas}}) + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O ({{abbr|l|liquid}})

当其中的碱是[[氢氧化钡|Ba(OH)<sub>2</sub>]] 时，可以在溶液中得到高氙酸钡晶体。<ref name="harding2002"/>

==高氙酸==
{{main|高氙酸}}
[[File:Perxenonsäure_Structural_Formula_V.1.svg|thumb]]
高氙酸是高氙酸根不稳定的共轭酸，由[[四氧化氙|四氧化氙]]在[[水|水]]中形成。它没有作为游离酸被分离出来，因为在酸性条件下它会迅速分解成[[三氧化氙|三氧化氙]]和[[氧气|氧气]]：<ref name="klaening">{{Cite journal | last1 = Klaening | first1 = U. K.|last2 = Appelman | first2 =E. H.| title = Protolytic properties of perxenic acid| journal = Inorganic Chemistry | volume = 27 | issue = 21| pages = 3760–3762 | date=October 1988 | doi = 10.1021/ic00294a018}}</ref><ref>{{Holleman&Wiberg|page=400}}</ref>
: 2 {{chem|HXeO|6|3-}} + 6 {{chem|H|+}} → 2 {{chem|XeO|3}} + 4 {{chem|H|2|O}} + {{chem|O|2}}

高氙酸的[[pKa|p''K''<sub>a</sub>]] 已间接计算，数值低于0，使其成为极强的酸。它的第一次去质子化会产生 {{chem|H|3|XeO|6|-}}， p''K''<sub>a</sub> 为 4.29，仍然相对的酸。两次去质子化物种 {{chem|H|2|XeO|6|2-}} 的 p''K''<sub>a</sub> 为 10.81。<ref>{{cite book
| title = Advances in Inorganic Chemistry
| volume = 46
| author1 = John H. Holloway
| author2 = Eric G. Hope
| editor = A. G. Sykes
| publisher = Academic Press
| year = 1998
| isbn = 0-12-023646-X
| page = 67
}}</ref> 然而，由于高氙酸在如上所述的酸性条件下快速分解，因此最常见的高氙酸盐带有阴离子 {{chem|XeO|6|4-}}。<ref name="klaening" /><ref name="wiberg" />

==性质==
高氙酸和阴离子 {{chem|XeO|6|4-}} 都是强[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]，<ref name="holcomb">{{Cite journal| first1 = H. P. | title = Analytical Oxidation of Americium with Sodium Perxenate | journal = Analytical Chemistry | volume = 37| issue = 3 | page = 415| last1 = Holcomb | date=March 1965 | doi = 10.1021/ac60222a002}}</ref>可以把银(I)氧化成银(III)，把铜(II)氧化成铜(III)，<ref name="bard1" />以及把锰(II)氧化成[[高锰酸盐|高锰酸盐]]。<ref>{{cite book
| title = General Chemistry
| author = Linus Pauling
| edition = 3rd
| publisher = Courier Dover Publications
| year = 1988
| isbn = 0-486-65622-5
| page = [https://archive.org/details/generalchemistry00paul_0/page/251 251]
| url-access = registration
| url = https://archive.org/details/generalchemistry00paul_0/page/251
}}</ref>高氙酸盐在酸性环境下不稳定，<ref name="bard1" />会立刻被还原成 {{chem|HXeO|4|-}}。<ref name="cotton1">{{Cotton&Wilkinson6th|page=593}}</ref>

高氙酸的[[高氙酸钠|钠]]、[[高氙酸钾|钾]]和[[高氙酸钡|钡]]盐可溶。<ref>{{cite book
| title = Concise encyclopedia chemistry
| url = https://archive.org/details/conciseencyclope00eagl
| author = Thomas Scott
| author2 = Mary Eagleson
| publisher = Walter de Gruyter
| year = 1994
| isbn = 3-11-011451-8
| page = 1183
}}</ref> 高氙酸钡溶液是合成[[四氧化氙|四氧化氙]] (XeO<sub>4</sub>) 的起始材料，方法是将其与浓[[硫酸|硫酸]]混合：<ref>{{cite book
| title = Elements of the ''p'' block
| url = https://archive.org/details/elementspblock00hard
| author = Charlie Harding
| author2 = David Arthur Johnson
| author3 = Rob Janes
| location = Great Britain
| publisher = Royal Society of Chemistry
| year = 2002
| isbn = 0-85404-690-9
| pages = [https://archive.org/details/elementspblock00hard/page/n93 92]–93
}}</ref>
: Ba<sub>2</sub>XeO<sub>6</sub> (s) + 2 H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> (l) →  XeO<sub>4</sub> (g) + 2 BaSO<sub>4</sub> (s) + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O (l)

大部分金属的高氙酸盐稳定，会剧烈分解的高氙酸银除外。<ref name="bard1">{{cite book
